'''Gazerfish''' is a {{Rarity|Common}} fish found in the [[Desolate Deep]]'s [[Desolate Deep#Brine Pool|Brine Pool]].

== Description ==
{{Description|The Gazerfish is a fast-moving prey fish within the Brine Pool of the Desolate Deep. They have a singular large eyeball on the front of their bodies, which they can close to disguise themselves from possible predators during the night. When they are most active during the day, they swim near the surface looking for smaller creatures to feed on.|Bestiary Entry}}

